honey roasted potatoes photo allrecipes.co.uk There are different ways to cook your potatoes and making it as honey roasted potatoes is one amazing way. Honey roasted potatoes are perfectly tender with just the right mix of flavors. Listed below are the ingredients needed to make this meal and the method used. Ingredients Preheat oven Chop and season potatoes with all the ingredients above. Saute for a while so it can cook faster. Wrap the potatoes in a foil paper and bake in the oven at 190 degrees till it cooks. check the potatoes by poking with a skewer to see it is done. Serve hot!